---
title: Cheesy Garlic Pull-Apart Rolls with Roasted Tomato Salsa | 12 Rolls
description: These cheesy garlic pull-apart rolls are the perfect party starter, oozing with cheese and infused with aromatic garlic and
parsley. Pair them with a tangy tomato relish that adds a delightful zing to each bite!
